lead_paragraph: German midfielder Ilkay Guendogan has joined Manchester City from Bundesliga side Borussia Dortmund on a four-year deal, the Premier League club announced on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Man City Sign Midfielder Guendogan From Dortmund
headline.main: Man City Sign Midfielder Guendogan From Dortmund
